<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,325,1910,1936]" pageId="6" pageNumber="164">Etymology</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[189,1399,1956,2018]" pageId="6" pageNumber="164">
The species epithet is a patronym in honour of the dipterist Dr Joachim Ziegler (
<collectingRegion box="[1141,1218,1956,1983]" country="Germany" name="Berlin" pageId="6" pageNumber="164">Berlin</collectingRegion>
) who collected the 
<typeStatus box="[233,340,1992,2018]" pageId="6" pageNumber="164">holotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
